name: Unique Knits Logo Snapback
description: Unique Knits Logo hat with a red bill, green underbill, and mint head space. The front of the hat has our Unique Knits logo in acrylic.

name: Unique Knits "All Black Everything" logo Snapback (Limited Edition)
description: Limited Edition Series 5 "All Black Everything" UK logo snapback. This one of a kind Unique Knits Hat has a leather bill with a retro green underbill. Also on the face of the hat is our Unique Knits tilted robot head logo in acrylic.  Embroidered on the left side of the hat are five stripes in red, these stripes represent when the name Unique Knits was created, which was in 2005. The stripes also represent the five characters of the Unique Knits brand, these characters names are: Knits, Nicco, Inzzo, Tego, and our girl character whos' name is yet to be reveled. We hope you enjoy this piece of Unique history as much as we do. Welcome To Our World!!

name: Unique Knits Robo logo Wood Bracelet

name: Ladies Unique Knits Super Inzzo Tee
description: Unique Knits Super Inzzo Tee, Cut for the ladies. Of course the idea came from Superman, but we decided to use our very own character Inzzo with our logo on his chest.

name: Ladies Unique Knits E.T. Tego Tee
description: Unique Knits famous E.T. Tego Tee, Cut just for the ladies. This special tee is an illustration of one of our favorite movies with a Unique Knits spin to it, using our characters Tego and Nicco the monkey.

name: Ladies Unique Knits Lazer Logo Tee
description: Unique Knits Lazer Logo Tee, cut just for the women. A Black tee with our tilted robot head logo on the front in Yellow, blue, Green, and Red.

name: Retro Running Inzzo Heather Grey/Black
description: As the Unique Knits brand continues to grow, the characters do as well. One of Unique Knits goals is to always innovate and never be the same. To be Unique is to be different. With the popularity of the Running Inzzo tee we have decided to continue to make this tee in its regular form as when it was first made, but retro it do to popular demand. Another reason for the decision to retro this tee is because of the recreation of our character Inzzo. Both styles of the Running Inzzo tee will be sold on our site the old and new, just the old one will be retro now. So we hope you enjoy this capsule tee just like we do. Welcome To Our World!!
